-- Ecuador Average Company Bond Yield Rose to 8.07% in First Half
-- B y   N a t h a n   G i l l
-- 2012-07-12T19:26:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-12/ecuador-average-company-bond-yield-rose-to-8-07-in-first-half.html
The average yield for Ecuadorean
corporate bonds sold in local markets rose to 8.07 percent in
first six months of the year, the Bolsa de Valores de Quito said
today in a report on its  website .  The average corporate yield was 7.99 percent in the first
half of 2011, according to the exchange.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nathan Gill in Quito at 
